Package com.lukeleber.scandroid.sae.j1979 Description

Artifacts modeled after the information contained in SAE-J1979 ("E/E Diagnostic Test Modes") can be found within this package. Two types of terminology are provided by the artifacts of this package:
  1. Standard terminology (per SAE-J1979)
  2. "User Friendly" terminology (internationalized, no abbreviations and/or acronyms)

Standard terminology is provided by the Object.toString() method, whereas the user-friendly terminology is provided by the Internationalized.toI18NString(android.content.Context) method.
